### Design choices\par
The beginning of the design process was the bookWorm brand logo which uses a strong blue. From this to provide a fresh look I chose a palette based on shades of blue and green selected using the palette tool at [Coolors)(). Many aspects of the design use bootstrap components for consistency but to give a modern look they have been restyled as, for example, the navbar toggler button which has no border in order to give it a more contemporary look. The font choice for the logo, was determined by experimentation using [Fontastic]() and provides an appealing visual pun.  The design seeks to provide a visually consistent, responsive and easy to navigate user experience.\par
